## <a id='intro'></a> About <%= vars.segment_runtime_full %>

The <%= vars.segment_runtime_full %> <%= vars.v_major_version %> tile is available for installation with <%= vars.ops_manager %> v2.10.

Isolation segments provide dedicated pools of resources where you can deploy apps and isolate workloads. Using isolation segments separates app resources as completely as if they were in different deployments but avoids redundant management and network complexity. For more information about isolation segments, see [Isolation Segments](../../concepts/security.html#isolation-segments) in _<%= vars.app_runtime_abbr %> Security_.

For more information about using isolation segments in your deployment, see [Managing Isolation Segments](../../adminguide/isolation-segments.html).


